Title: The ${\mathscr P}(\varphi)_2$ Model on the de Sitter Space
Authors: João C. A. Barata and Christian D. Jäkel and Jens Mund
Abstract: In 1975 by Figari, H{\o}egh-Krohn and Nappi constructed the ${\mathscr P}(\varphi)_2$ model on the two-dimensional de Sitter space. Here we complement their work with a number of new results.
